WEBVTT

1
00:00:13.733 --> 00:00:15.800
Xia Xiner, where is the chicken?

2
00:00:15.866 --> 00:00:18.266
Prepare me a month's traveler's check

3
00:00:18.333 --> 00:00:20.200
Prepare another ticket for me to go abroad

4
00:00:20.200 --> 00:00:21.100
Oh, right.

5
00:00:21.766 --> 00:00:23.566
Bring me Xia Rulian too

6
00:00:24.133 --> 00:00:25.800
I want him to kneel down and apologize to me

7
00:00:25.800 --> 00:00:28.500
I'm where I am today because of him

8
00:00:28.500 --> 00:00:29.433
otherwise

9
00:00:30.766 --> 00:00:32.666
This little bastard will not live

10
00:00:32.666 --> 00:00:34.366
I can prepare both checks and boat tickets

11
00:00:34.366 --> 00:00:37.400
But I'm going to have an end between us

12
00:00:42.133 --> 00:00:45.466
Your mother is coming to save you.

13
00:00:47.333 --> 00:00:50.400
Mom and Dad, baby, don't be afraid.

14
00:00:50.400 --> 00:00:53.566
Xia Ruoyan, you are really mother and son

15
00:00:53.566 --> 00:00:54.866
Trying to save him

16
00:00:55.333 --> 00:00:56.833
Kneel down for me now

17
00:00:57.166 --> 00:00:59.500
Otherwise, I can't guarantee it.

18
00:00:59.733 --> 00:01:01.400
What would I do to him?

19
00:01:01.400 --> 00:01:03.766
Next star, before you say or do anything

20
00:01:03.766 --> 00:01:05.200
You'd better weigh it first

21
00:01:05.200 --> 00:01:06.200
Lu Tingyue

22
00:01:06.866 --> 00:01:08.200
You have some power

23
00:01:08.200 --> 00:01:10.666
Your son is in my hands now.

24
00:01:10.666 --> 00:01:12.300
Next star you do all this

25
00:01:12.300 --> 00:01:14.133
Do you think you'll make it out alive?

26
00:01:14.133 --> 00:01:16.266
This is what you forced me to do

27
00:01:18.266 --> 00:01:19.066
I Kneel

28
00:01:19.666 --> 00:01:21.033
Don't hurt Xiao Qi here

